    "body": "> Are you using a two-line prompt?\r\n\r\n@chipbuster This may be the cause. I'm using Warp besides of Terminal. Warp's prompt and commands are separated so if you press `cmd + k`, the prompt stayed the same.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1038\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/starship/starship/assets/31413093/4d1b5b72-5904-4852-9d01-8a6327d9e37a\">\r\n\r\nBut here's the thing: The commands you type is not located beside the green arrow... 🤣 ",
